title: Natural Gas Heat, Wall-to-wall carpet, Disability Access
description: Welcome to Greenwich Place apartments in West Warwick, RI — where floor plans, amenities, and location meet to provide our residents with the living space that matches their lifestyle! Whether you're taking a dip in our inviting pool or entertaining guests in our contemporary clubhouse, every day at Greenwich Place speaks of home. Enjoy our state-of-the-art fitness center, take a stroll through the nearby parks, or enjoy the sunset from your private balcony or patio. Browse our gallery of photos for a closer glimpse of our West Warwick apartments and see for yourself the details of bright, beautiful interiors with vaulted ceilings, our up-to-date renovated kitchens and bathrooms, and our natural gas fireplaces complete with an exquisite built-in entertainment center. Our apartments also come equipped with a washer and dryer, making your apartment feel more like a home. We are a pet-friendly community, accepting both cats and dogs, so feel free to bring your furry friends along with you. Our residents love our amenities including the convenience we offer for online payments, online work orders, and of course the 24-hour maintenance we provide. Location is important, and we're only minutes from Providence with its numerous options for shopping, dining, and entertainment. Visit Federal Hill, take in inspiring art and music at Gallery Night, and don’t miss out on gondola rides during WaterFire and ice skating at the City Center. Ramble through Waterfront Park, take in the city's landmarks along Waterfront Park, and learn a little history at the same time. Whether you are commuting or simply need to head out of state, our easy access to Routes 295 and 95, and TF Green Airport will help you get you where you need to go. Living at Greenwich Place means you’re close to everything that’s important, in an apartment with everything you need! Check out our floor plans to see what’s currently available, and contact us today to set up a personal tour. Greenwich Place — West Warwick apartment living made simple.
-Natural Gas Fireplace with Built-in Entertainment Center

Enjoy our state-of-the-art fitness center, take a stroll through the nearby parks, or enjoy the sunset from your private balcony or patio. Browse our gallery of photos for a closer glimpse of our West Warwick apartments and see for yourself the details of bright, beautiful interiors with vaulted ceilings, our up-to-date renovated kitchens and bathrooms, and our natural gas fireplaces complete with an exquisite built-in entertainment center. Our apartments also come equipped with a washer and dryer, making your apartment feel more like a home. We are a pet-friendly community, accepting both cats and dogs, so feel free to bring your furry friends along with you. Our residents love our amenities including the convenience we offer for online payments, online work orders, and of course the 24-hour maintenance we provide. Location is important, and we're only minutes from Providence with its numerous options for shopping, dining, and entertainment. Visit Federal Hill, take in inspiring art and music at Gallery Night, and don’t miss out on gondola rides during WaterFire and ice skating at the City Center. Ramble through Waterfront Park, take in the city's landmarks along Waterfront Park, and learn a little history at the same time. Whether you are commuting or simply need to head out of state, our easy access to Routes 295 and 95, and TF Green Airport will help you get you where you need to go. Living at Greenwich Place means you’re close to everything that’s important, in an apartment with everything you need! Check out our floor plans to see what’s currently available, and contact us today to set up a personal tour. Greenwich Place — West Warwick apartment living made simple.

Centrally located in the heart of Kent County, Shady Oaks Apartments in Warwick RI offers all of the conveniences of in-town living in a quiet secluded neighborhood hideaway. Treat yourself to the lifestyle you deserve by enjoying your free time in our beautifully landscaped, peaceful community knowing that all of the wonderful attractions Rhode Island has to offer are right at your fingertips. With convenient access to all major highways, close proximity to retail-filled Bald Hill Road and our famed beaches and state parks just a short drive away, our location simply can’t be more convenient.

Our thoughtfully designed apartment homes keep comfort and convenience in mind. Our apartments feature new granite countertops, abundant closet space, fully-equipped kitchens and spacious layouts making home furnishing care-free and fun-filled.

Enjoy the sunshine relaxing by our refreshing swimming pool, challenge your friends to a game on our full-sized basketball court or simply spend some time admiring the views in the shade under our prestigious oak trees.
Community fee of $25 monthly to cover the cost of heat and hot water, snow and trash removal, and parking. Tenant responsible for any electric/cable charges incurred.

title: 2 bdrm with large yard!
description: This two-bedroom apartment is on the ground floor in an owner-occupied two-family. Rent includes heat, hot water, and trash. All you have to pay is electricity. Recently renovated in 2016, this apartment has all hardwood floors, gorgeous new stainless steel appliances, and granite countertops. Has washer and dryer hookup in the unit. There is only one off-street parking spot, but we could squeeze in a second car in the event of a snowstorm where you can’t park on the street. Please no dogs, we would consider a cat. Absolutely no smoking in the apartment.

We also have a pug that is very friendly who would be out in the yard at times. Please email me with a little about yourself and your phone number so we can arrange a time for a phone interview. References are required and will be checked.
